plot: Jaye and Eric help Katya, who's come all the way from Russia to get married to "Peter". The groom-to-be turns out to be 13.

Jaye and Eric start to get closer while helping a Russian woman who came to America to meet her online fiancé Peter, who turns out to be less than she expected. Meanwhile, Peter falls hard for Jaye and will do anything to keep Eric away from her.—Anonymous
